<section class="audit-summary">
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            审计概览
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>您所审计的工程总共有 <strong><%- audit.summary.total %></strong> 个风险漏洞。</p>
            
            <div class="summary-grid">
                <div class="summary-item critical">
                    <div><%- desc.severityLevels.critical %>漏洞</div>
                    <div class="count"><%- audit.summary.critical %></div>
                    <div>个</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="summary-item high">
                    <div><%- desc.severityLevels.high %>漏洞</div>
                    <div class="count"><%- audit.summary.high %></div>
                    <div>个</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="summary-item moderate">
                    <div><%- desc.severityLevels.moderate %>漏洞</div>
                    <div class="count"><%- audit.summary.moderate %></div>
                    <div>个</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="summary-item low">
                    <div><%- desc.severityLevels.low %>漏洞</div>
                    <div class="count"><%- audit.summary.low %></div>
                    <div>个</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="severity-explanation">
                <h3>漏洞等级说明</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong><%- desc.severityLevels.critical %>漏洞</strong>被认为是极其严重的，应该立即修复。</li>
                    <li><strong><%- desc.severityLevels.high %>漏洞</strong>被认为是严重的，应该尽快修复。</li>
                    <li><strong><%- desc.severityLevels.moderate %>漏洞</strong>被认为是中等严重的，可以选择在时间允许时修复。</li>
                    <li><strong><%- desc.severityLevels.low %>漏洞</strong>被认为是轻微的，可以根据自行需要进行修复。</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>漏洞详细信息</h2>
    
    <% if (audit.summary.critical) { %>
        <%- include('./detail.ejs', {type:'critical'}); %>
    <% } %>
    
    <% if (audit.summary.high) { %>
        <%- include('./detail.ejs', {type:'high'}); %>
    <% } %>
    
    <% if (audit.summary.moderate) { %>
        <%- include('./detail.ejs', {type:'moderate'}); %>
    <% } %>
    
    <% if (audit.summary.low) { %>
        <%- include('./detail.ejs', {type:'low'}); %> 
    <% } %>
</section>